# E2E Test Reports

This directory contains generated test reports and artifacts.

## Contents

- **report.html** - HTML test report with pass/fail results and output
- **screenshots/** - Screenshots captured on test failures
- **videos/** - Screen recordings of failed tests (if enabled)

## Generated Files

All files in this directory are automatically generated during test execution and should not be committed to version control.

## Viewing Reports

Open `report.html` in any web browser to view the latest test results.
